                                    <rect key="frame" x="20" y="716" width="972" height="33.5"/>
                                    <string key="text">Erase all PIN is a PIN code that destroys all user data if you enter it on startup. It is like the Clear All button above but can be entered in the PIN dialog. Everything will be erased without asking for confirmation.</string>
